The paper discusses personalized ranking and recommender systems in e-commerce, which are typically studied in the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of contextual data, which falls under the sub-categories of Cybersecurity (cs.CY) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). Finally, the paper discusses user engagement and online testing, which are typically studied in the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category.
